### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### ============================================
### Main Page
### ============================================

### Get Main Page (index.html)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ============================================
### Product Operations
### ============================================

### Load Products from Database (POST - loads from Postgres)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/load?sortBy=id&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### Get Products with Pagination and Sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=id&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10

### Get Products - Sort by Title (Ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=title&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10

### Get Products - Sort by Price (Descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=price&order=desc&page=0&pageSize=50

### Get Products - Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=id&order=asc&page=1&pageSize=10

### ============================================
### Add Product
### ============================================

### Add New Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=id&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

title=Test Product&price=99.99&vendor=Test Vendor

### Add Product (Minimal - Title Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=id&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

title=Another Product

### ============================================
### Search Products
### ============================================

### Search Page
GET {{baseUrl}}/search

### Search Products by Title
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?query=test&sortBy=id&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10

### Search Products - Empty Query (Returns All)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?query=&sortBy=id&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10

### Search Products - Sort by Price
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?query=product&sortBy=price&order=desc&page=0&pageSize=50

### ============================================
### Edit Product
### ============================================

### Get Edit Product Page (Replace {id} with actual product ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1/edit

### Update Product (Replace {id} with actual product ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/1/update
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

title=Updated Product Title&price=149.99&vendor=Updated Vendor

### ============================================
### Delete Product
### ============================================

### Delete Product (Replace {id} with actual product ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/1/delete?sortBy=id&order=asc&page=0&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

### ============================================
### Notes:
### - Replace {id} with actual product IDs from your database
### - All POST requests return HTML fragments (Thymeleaf templates)
### - Responses will be HTML, not JSON (since this is a server-side rendered app)
### - Make sure your Spring Boot app is running on port 8081
### ============================================
